.SH NAME
Mochi::FS::PackFile \- \fBPackFile\fP is a class with two purposes\&. First, it implements \fBIFileLoader\fP, allowing to be used as a simple file system\&. Second, it has the Pack and Unpack methods, used to create \&.pak files, used by this file system\&. Creating \&.pak files has several benefits\&. The first one is obfuscation, making it more difficult to end users to get access to your game assets\&. The second one is being loaded as a stream, as it allows to only load what is needed at the moment\&. It also is easily extended to, for example, zip all or only specific files, reducing final build size\&. Ownership:  

